                     ; coordinates (an enemy ship launching EscapePod/Cargo,
                     ; which inherits coordinates, OCS and speed from the
                     ; parent)
 $F55B JR $F501      ; place a Cargo object in space at the player's
                     ; coordinates into a free slot

